---
// Fondo minimalista: solo orbes de luz muy suaves para dar profundidad
// al degradado, sin elementos que compitan con el titular.
---

<div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="absolute -right-32 -top-32 h-[34rem] w-[34rem] rounded-full bg-brand-200/30 blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute right-1/4 top-1/3 h-[26rem] w-[26rem] rounded-full bg-brand-100/20 blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute -bottom-40 right-10 h-[30rem] w-[30rem] rounded-full bg-white/10 blur-3xl"></div>
</div>
